            "id": 6320226,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 達發(6526)股價拉至漲停，漲停價470.5元，成交1,291張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>達發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6526:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6526\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6526-TW</a>)23日12:35上漲42.5元，股價漲停報470.5元，委買123張，成交1,291張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為無線通訊晶片。固網通訊晶片。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>達發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6526:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6526\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6526-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌2.73%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.04%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-179 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-171 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+8 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-16 張</li> <li>融資增減：-22 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
